Author: fac_ade
Text: Wait so it's temporary? Cause mines been gone a few days and I barely purged back then too lol, I'm worried it's never coming back :(

Author: DogTeeth_Val
Text: Bulimic episodes often result in the temporary loss of ones gag reflex. When we indulge in our disordered behaviours our body will fight back like that, this is a sign that you're pushing yourself too hard right now.
